        <title>World Explore Template</title>
        <description>A template for an activity to learn about a certain topic all
        around the world. Simply follow the instructions to create locations, then
        enter all content in the file located in resources called content.txt</description>
        <prerequisite>None</prerequisite>
        <goal>To explore ________ around the world!</goal>
        <manual>
        The objective of the game is to visit every location, learn the topic,
       	and correctly answer the question. For each location that you've answered
       	the question correctly, the travel bar at the bottom of the screen will increase.
       	Win the game by visiting all locations and correctly answering all questions!</manual>
